00:07:03.930 --> 00:07:05.597
Do we have a solution?

00:07:06.297 --> 00:07:09.430
What are we to do?
We are faced with a paradox.

00:07:10.397 --> 00:07:12.697
Less and less phosphorus
will be available.

00:07:12.963 --> 00:07:16.163
